WEBVTT

00:08.273 --> 00:11.693
Today, more than ever, we communicate on a global scale.

00:12.421 --> 00:14.925
We interact with people from all walks of life.

00:15.693 --> 00:20.940
And we operate in very different linguistic, social and cultural universes.

00:21.527 --> 00:24.308
In this context, successful communication stands out...

00:24.651 --> 00:28.146
...as a key component of companies facing new challenges...

00:28.454 --> 00:33.899
...in a constant search to improve their agility, responsiveness and competitiveness.

00:34.233 --> 00:36.875
Effective communication nurtures cohesion,...

00:37.430 --> 00:41.313
...develops a sense of belonging and enhances performance,...

00:41.725 --> 00:44.533
...both for the individual and for the company.

00:45.071 --> 00:48.777
Telelangue, in its mission of communication facilitator...

00:49.179 --> 00:52.635
...supports you in your strategy to communicate better...

00:52.844 --> 00:56.306
...at every level. Our strength is our experience.

00:56.411 --> 01:00.493
Forty years of expertise, 600 communication facilitators...

01:00.797 --> 01:03.109
...and thousands and thousands of hours of training.

01:03.603 --> 01:07.499
Our know-how is centered on three areas of expertise:...

01:07.999 --> 01:11.361
...Linguistical skills, social skills and intercultural skills.

01:11.990 --> 01:17.320
Telelangue is the facilitating partner you need to open up the field of possibilities...

01:17.564 --> 01:21.313
...and to expand the scope and impact of your communication...

01:21.889 --> 01:24.538
...in a world of perpetual interaction.

